  author = {Arsen ABDULALI and Stefano DI PASCOLI and Gonçalo ADELINO and Alexander DIEDRICH and Bilal AHMAD and Xiaochen DONG and Adel ALAEDDINI and Valentina DONZELLA and Jose María ALVAREZ and Roman DUMITRESCU and Gerasimos ARVANITIS and Hans EHM and Virendra ASHIWAL and Elisabet ESTÉVEZ ESTÉVEZ and Heitor ASSUMPÇÃO and Neil EVANS and Carlo Alberto AVIZZANO and Syed Hasib Akhter FARUQUI and Kaja BALZEREIT and André FISCHER and Máté BANCSICS and Juliane FISCHER and Ayan BANERJEE and Enrico FRACCAROLI and Jyotsna BAPAT and Jörg FRANKE and Giacomo BARBIERI and Attila FRANKÓ and Gabriele BARIS and Franco FUMMI and Ozkan BEBEK and Marco GABICCINI and Yvonne BERGMANN and Kevin GALASSI and Luca BEUGGERT and Frank GÄRTNER and Carlos GEORGE THURUTHEL BOCANEGRA GALLARDO and Malte BUHR and Lorenzo GIGLI and Andreas BUNTE and Kieran GILDAY and Rogerio CAMPOS-REBELO and Denis GÖLLNER and Alessio CAPORALI and Ricardo GOMES and Tiago CARVALHO and Simon GRAU and Suleyman Can ÇEVIK and Christoph GRIMM and Pak Hung CHAN and Karl GRITZ and Michael CHAPPELL and Sandeep GUPTA and Jicheng CHEN and Antonio Manuel GUTIERREZ and Wei-hsun CHIANG and Sasirekha GVK and Alessandro CIMATTI and Fabian HABEN and Andrea CIRILLO and Mehrtash HARANDI and Michael COLOMBO and Joseph HARDWICKE and Sandor DALECKE and Alexander HAYWARD and Nicola DALL'ORA and René HEESCH and Salvatore D'ARCO and Csaba HEGEDŰS and Javier DE LAS MORENAS and Albert HEIM and Alexandre DE OLIVEIRA JÚNIOR and David HERMANN and Miguel DELGADO-PRIETO and Gereon HINZ and Jerker DELSING and Mario HOERNICKE and Mustafa DERMAN and Simon HOFMANN and Patrick DEUTSCHMANN and Gergely HOLLOSI and Jan van DEVENTER and Peter HOPKINSON},
